it is single node cluster 1node=mastenode+workernode(both same)
https://v1-18.docs.kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-minikube/

1. to install minicube on windows which hyperviser supports ? hyperv,oracle virtualbox


2. to install minicube on linux which hypervisor supports ? kvm , virtualbox 
