## kubeadm

ref : https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/production-environment/tools/kubeadm/install-kubeadm/
multi node cluster (multiple worker and master node separaty)

requirements :
master node should be min 2 gb ram and 2 cpu 20gb hardisk
worker node 2gb 1 cpu  20gb hdd
swap memory should be off --> bcz kuberneties not allow you to store runtime data in swap .. only allow in save in ram
should install docker ,kubeadm,kubelet,kubectl install
docker -> for container creation
kubeadm ->cluster setup
kubectl --> cluster component management,
kubectl --> command line


systemctl status firewall -> check firewall status

interview: ports used by which service 

kya kubernet ke component os ke upar chalte hai ya pod -> pod ke upar
	

